<plot>Billy and the Kid is a modern Western about Billy, a 70 year-old security guard, in a Western-themed highway attraction. When a rock band comes to town, they begin to terrorize the small community, vandalizing the stores and disrespecting the shopkeepers. As band begins to take-over, the towns-people look to Billy, their security guard. But what can Billy, a 70 year-old man without a gun, do to stop these rowdy strangers?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?070970</url></doc>
